<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <title>VDI nachrichten - Das Nachrichtenportal für Ingenieure</title>
    <meta name="description" content="VDI nachrichten bieten Fachinformationen für Ingenieure und technische Fach- und Führungskräfte rund um Technik, Wirtschaft, Gesellschaft."/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Source Sans Pro", sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 600px;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 10vh auto 0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 10px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: lighter;
        }

        .headline {
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 100%;
            width: 300px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.55;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .button {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border: 0;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #004a82;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0 50px;
            text-align: center;
            height: 70px;
            line-height: 70px;
            border-radius: 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #00345b;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .footer a {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

